---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="New Patients — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Start your smile journey at Oasis Dental Care in Huntington Beach. Learn what to expect as a new patient, read FAQs, and access patient forms."
  page="new-patients"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="tag">/ New Patients</span>
    <h1>Start Your Smile Journey Here</h1>
    <p>Whether this is your first dental visit in years or your very first time at Oasis, we've made it easy to know what to expect — and even easier to get started.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request an appointment <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Quick links bar -->
<div class="page-links">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a href="#comfort">Care &amp; Comfort</a>
    <a href="#faq">New Patient FAQ</a>
    <a href="#forms">Patient Forms</a>
    <a href="/contact">Book Now</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Care & Comfort -->
<section class="pad" id="comfort">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="np-split reveal">
      <div class="np-copy">
        <span class="tag">Care &amp; Comfort</span>
        <h2>A Calm, Supportive Approach</h2>

        <div class="comfort-block">
          <div class="comfort-item">
            <div class="comfort-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Dental anxiety</strong> is more common than most people realize, and it affects patients of all ages. From the moment you arrive, our goal is to create a sense of ease.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comfort-item">
            <div class="comfort-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M9 12h6M12 9v6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Gentle techniques and modern tools</strong> matter as much as the quality of your treatment. These technologies let us show you what we see, making your treatment options easier to understand.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comfort-item">
            <div class="comfort-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>You set the pace, judgement-free.</strong> Every patient has a different comfort level, and we honor that. Likewise, life gets busy. Anxiety happens. Sometimes years pass between dental visits—and that's okay. This is a place where you are welcomed—not judged.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="np-media">
        <div class="ph-block">
          <div class="ph-inner">
            <div class="ph-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ph-title">Welcome area photo</div>
            <div class="ph-sub">Placeholder — add a photo of your reception or treatment room here.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ph-stat">
            <div><span class="n">4.8★</span><span class="l">Patient rated</span></div>
            <div><span class="n">25+</span><span class="l">Years experience</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="pad np-faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="tag">FAQ</span>
        <h2>Frequent Questions About New Patients</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="np-faq-layout reveal">
      <div class="faq">
        <details open>
          <summary>What happens during my first appointment?</summary>
          <p>You'll meet with Dr. Fu for a conversation about your dental history, followed by an exam and any needed digital x-rays or scans. We'll review what we see together and talk about your options in clear, simple terms.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Will I get a cleaning at my first visit?</summary>
          <p>In most cases, yes. If a different type of cleaning or treatment is needed first, we'll explain why and help you plan the next steps.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What if I'm nervous about dental visits?</summary>
          <p>You're not alone. We take your comfort seriously and go at your pace. Dr. Fu checks in often, explains each step, and adjusts treatment based on your needs.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What should I bring with me?</summary>
          <p>Please bring a photo ID, your dental insurance card (if you have one), and any recent dental records if available. If not, no problem—we'll take care of everything here.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Does Dr. Fu explain treatment options?</summary>
          <p>Absolutely. Clear communication is one of our core values. We walk you through each recommendation and help you understand what is necessary, optional, or can wait.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Can I talk to Dr. Fu about past dental experiences or concerns?</summary>
          <p>Yes—please do. Understanding your past experiences helps us tailor your care and create a visit that feels comfortable and reassuring.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="np-faq-aside">
        <div class="np-aside-card">
          <div class="hd">
            <div class="grid-ov"></div>
            <h3>Ready to get started?</h3>
            <p>New patients are always welcome. Book online or give us a call.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
              <span>Same-week appointments often available</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              <span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified up front</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg>
              <span>ADA, CDC &amp; OSHA safety protocols</span>
            </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request appointment</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Patient Forms -->
<section class="pad" id="forms">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="forms-layout reveal">
      <div class="forms-info">
        <span class="tag">Patient Forms</span>
        <h2 class="forms-h2">Before your visit.</h2>
        <p>Please do not email completed forms, as standard email is not a secure method for transmitting personal health information. Simply bring the completed forms with you to your scheduled appointment, or arrive a few minutes early to complete them in the office.</p>
        <div class="forms-note">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 8v4M12 16h.01"/></svg>
          <span>Forms will be available here soon. In the meantime, you're welcome to call us and we'll prepare everything ahead of your visit.</span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:28px">
          <a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call to prepare your visit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="forms-placeholder">
        <div class="fp-inner">
          <div class="fp-ic">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14,2 14,8 20,8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10,9 9,9 8,9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="fp-title">Patient Forms</div>
          <div class="fp-sub">Coming soon — forms will be available for download here.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ctacard reveal">
      <div class="grid-ov"></div>
      <div class="c">
        <span class="tag">New patients welcome</span>
        <h2>Ready when you are.</h2>
        <p>Tell us a good time and someone warm will get back to you — usually the same day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acts">
        <a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
        <a class="btn btn-o" href="/contact">Request online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
#comfort { padding-bottom: 80px; }

/* split layout */
.np-split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: stretch;
}
@media(max-width: 880px) {
  .np-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
}
.np-copy h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 44px);
  margin-top: 14px;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}

/* comfort items */
.comfort-block {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 22px;
  margin-top: 28px;
}
.comfort-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 44px 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  align-items: start;
  padding: 20px;
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line-l);
  border-radius: 12px;
}
.comfort-item div:last-child {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.comfort-item strong {
  color: var(--ink);
}
.comfort-ic {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 11px;
  background: rgba(11,129,116,.08);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.comfort-ic svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  stroke: var(--teal);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.7;
}

/* media placeholder */
.np-media { position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.ph-block {
  flex: 1;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,129,116,.04) 0 14px, transparent 14px 28px), var(--dark-2);
  border-radius: 18px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.ph-inner {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 24px;
  border: 1.5px dashed rgba(95,208,192,.32);
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px;
}
.ph-ic {
  width: 58px;
  height: 58px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(95,208,192,.4);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
}
.ph-ic svg {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}
.ph-title {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #eaf6f3;
}
.ph-sub {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: #86b3ab;
  max-width: 230px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.ph-stat {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 18px;
  left: 18px;
  right: 18px;
  background: rgba(8,34,31,.82);
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
}
.ph-stat .n {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--teal-300);
  display: block;
}
.ph-stat .l {
  font-size: 10.5px;
  color: #86b3ab;
  letter-spacing: .01em;
  margin-top: 3px;
  display: block;
}

/* faq section */
.np-faq-section {
  background: var(--dark);
  color: #eaf6f3;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.np-faq-section .shead h2 { color: #fff; }
.np-faq-section .tag { color: var(--teal-300); }
.np-faq-section .tag::before { background: var(--teal-300); }
.np-faq-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .7fr;
  gap: 40px;
  margin-top: 42px;
  align-items: start;
}
.np-faq-layout .faq { margin-top: 0; }
@media(max-width: 900px) {
  .np-faq-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* faq overrides for dark bg */
.np-faq-section .faq details {
  background: var(--dark-2);
  border-color: var(--line);
}
.np-faq-section .faq summary {
  color: #eaf6f3;
}
.np-faq-section .faq p {
  color: #a9ccc5;
}
.np-faq-section .faq summary::after { color: var(--teal-300); }

/* aside card */
.np-aside-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: var(--dark-2);
  overflow: hidden;
  position: sticky;
  top: 92px;
}
.np-aside-card .hd {
  background: var(--teal-700);
  padding: 22px 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.np-aside-card .hd h3 {
  position: relative;
  font-size: 19px;
  color: #fff;
}
.np-aside-card .hd p {
  position: relative;
  color: #d4f3ee;
  font-size: 13.5px;
  margin-top: 6px;
}
.np-aside-card .bd {
  padding: 22px 24px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}
.np-aside-card .row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  color: #a9ccc5;
}
.np-aside-card .row svg {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.7;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.np-aside-card .divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
}
.np-aside-card .btn {
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.np-aside-card .btn-out {
  background: transparent;
  color: #a9ccc5;
  border-color: var(--line);
}
.np-aside-card .btn-out:hover {
  color: #fff;
  border-color: var(--teal-300);
}

/* forms section */
.forms-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
  align-items: stretch;
}
.forms-info {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e4e8e7;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 44px 40px;
}
.forms-h2 {
  font-size: clamp(30px, 3.8vw, 46px);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  margin-top: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
@media(max-width: 860px) {
  .forms-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
.forms-info p {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.forms-note {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-top: 28px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  background: rgba(11,129,116,.07);
  border: 1px solid rgba(11,129,116,.18);
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.forms-note svg {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  stroke: var(--teal);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.7;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.forms-placeholder {
  flex: 1;
  min-height: 320px;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,129,116,.04) 0 14px, transparent 14px 28px), var(--dark-2);
  border-radius: 18px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.fp-inner {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 24px;
  border: 1.5px dashed rgba(95,208,192,.32);
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px;
}
.fp-ic {
  width: 58px;
  height: 58px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(95,208,192,.4);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
}
.fp-ic svg {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}
.fp-title {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: #fff;
}
.fp-sub {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: #9cc4bd;
  max-width: 220px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
</style>
